   _______________________________________________________________________

The Airborne Sensor Facility provides remote sensing systems development for
the Airborne Science Program; calibration and validation of the Earth
Observing System's earth science investigations; and system operation, data
processing, calibration and maintenance of Code Y facility remote sensing
instruments.

